AD | paid partnerships with @balibody 

You guys know how much I love Bali body and today I’m so pleased to be sharing the brand new product to their range ✨ the instant tan ✨

We’ve all had them last min plans pop up date nights/nights out and not having enough time to get our tan on or our tan is looking a little questionable so Bali body to the rescue to solve all of them problems 🙌🏻

This instant tan is one of the best, dries super fast, such a beaut golden colour that looks natural oh and the best part it doesn’t rub off of transfer 🙌🏻

It’s available now so get your hands on one of these. You won’t regret it 💕

We make content for brands, we make content for ourselves so it’s only right we started making content for weddings too ✨ 

Introducing your wedding content creation dream team - Jess & Tash!

With over a decade of experience creating content on our own socials and for brands, we kept being asked if we created content for weddings too and realised we absolutely should! Not Just Socials was always meant to be not JUST socials, but we felt the weddings needed their own place to shine so Afterglow was born. 🤍

We’ve already got a few dates locked in but if you’re a 2025/2026 bride we would LOVE to capture your day ✨
